game.name: Lizard Rocket
game.description:
Your lizard has turned into a rocket and wants to fly high in the sky. Do you want to help your friendly pet fly to the moon and make her dream come true? Join Lizard Rocket and allow yourself to make this cute and lovely lizard fly with rocket as high as possible! Try not to crash with any stone or rock falling downward at a regular interval to complete her flying journey successful! Do not forget to collect coins you see on the way to improve her power. 

Hold the LMB when you play on computer or tap the screen on mobile phone and get ready to take her right and left to avoid the obstacles! The coins you collect can also be used to provide her with the needful super powers like tiny feature, shield, and speed in this super fun distance game. It will be amazing to play the role of a lizard who wants to be on the top in the sky. You have to put your quick reflexes and avoiding skills to test to create the best score. 

Try to play wisely to fly as high as possible to beat your previous high score and set a new one! Good luck to browse through the huge puzzle challenges to meet the most desired ones!
